## Tuition Fee Loan

You could get a <%= format_money(tuition_fee_amount, pounds_only: true) %> [Tuition Fee Loan](<%= tuition_fee_url %>) each year to help pay your course tuition fees.

Depending on which course you’re studying and how much your course provider is charging, your Tuition Fee Loan may not be enough to cover the full cost of your course.

<% if studied_before %>
  If you’ve studied before, your loan might be less. Find out more about [how your entitlement is worked out](/student-finance-on-or-after-1-january-2027/eligibility).
<% end %>
